{
  "stem": "5357.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother, also, was caught to the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just came to the ghetto, and they caught people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or they had a list.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know my brother-in-law was no physical laborer, because he was short and he wasn't really too well.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they took him to be the administrator of the camp, and my sister went with him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when they caught my brother, they took him to the same camp in Karczew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was Yitzchak.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other one, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They caught both of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yitzchak was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was more flexible, so he adjusted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But Mottel, my other brother, the rabbi, he wasn't very flexible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he wouldn't-- the same thing-- he wouldn't eat what everybody did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had to have his own dishes and cook his own meals, to be sure that it's Kosher.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even in the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they send them out to build roads, because that's what this camp was for, to build roads for the tanks-- not for the tanks, for the motorcycle and trucks.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they didn't have paved roads in-- around Karczew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all muddy when it was raining, so they used to get stuck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what this crew was for.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a few hundred people that they were sent in different directions to build the road.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when my brother went on the road, he looked at his watch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was time to pray, so he stopped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here everybody yelled at him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're going to get killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he just wouldn't listen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was unfortunate that the day before the liquidation of the camp, he came home from--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the camp.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Karczew.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of Karczew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- oh, the city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're right, the city.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
